    ["D"] = "Tavara, one of our herbalists, has been gone far too long in her search for herbs.  I fear she is hurt and in need of help, yet I cannot look for her myself.$b$bPlease find her and lend your healing if needed, fellow $c.  She was heading east towards some hot springs when she left Azure Watch.",
