    ["D"] = "The orcish ruins of Zeth\'Gor to the southeast serve as a base for an ever-growing tide of orcs emerging from Hellfire Citadel.$B$BThe Sons of Lothar have been fighting them for some time, and the stories they tell would be nigh unbelievable if I hadn\'t seen these \'fel\' orcs with my own eyes.$B$BSomething has changed them, augmented them in a way we\'ve never seen before. We have to do anything we can to keep them from strengthening. Go to Zeth\'Gor and destroy any supplies you find there.",
