  [10061] = {
    ["D"] = "When the Bonechewer fel orcs attacked the Expedition Armory, the garrison there fell quickly.  The battle was bloody and fierce, and there were no survivors.$B$BAlthough the dead were buried, their spirits continue to haunt those ruins.  Of late, I have been receiving visions that these spirits may soon become a threat to Thrallmar.$B$BThere is only one course of action to take.  We must grant these spirits rest.  You must overcome them in battle.",
