  [10122] = {
    ["D"] = "Each day, Hellfire Citadel opens its gates, and more fel orcs pour out and into the camps they\'ve established along the ramparts south of the fortress.$B$BI dispatched one of my most capable scouts, Private Imarion, to track their movements, preparations and numbers, but he hasn\'t returned to report his findings.$B$BImarion was to focus his efforts on the northernmost camp along the Southern Rampart, near where it joined the Citadel. Find him, $N. Without his information, we\'re sitting ducks.",
