  [10560] = {
    ["D"] = "<The calming melodic tones projected by A\'dal become more hushed and somber.>$B$B<You are shown the large naaru structure known as Tempest Keep.  It is now inhabited by the forces of Kael\'thas and its power used for nefarious ends.  A\'dal promises you greater tasks once you\'ve done your part to take back Tempest Keep.>",
