  },
  [11200] = {
    ["D"] = "We\'ve gleaned as much as we can from the ruins of the inn. I\'m concerned about where the investigation will lead us from here, but we must know the truth.$B$BBetween the hoofprints and the shield with Mosarn\'s mark, I\'m lead to believe that the Grimtotems may have been involved. They\'ve recently established a settlement in the swamp, Blackhoof Village to the northeast. Travel to Blackhoof Village and search for more arms of Mosarn\'s manufacture.",
